source.name: Foreign Assistance Dashboard
source.description: The Foreign Assistance Dashboard aims to incorporate all U.S. Government (USG) foreign assistance budget, financial, program, and performance data in a standard format. It will enable users to track, analyze, and monitor aid investments over time from initial Congressional request to expenditure at the activity level.
